name: Duskfall Alters (Portraits)
description:
Duskfall Alters

THE MODEL THAT INSPIRED "EPIC MIX" because literally "EPIC TRAIN" is in Epic mix!

YOU CAN TEST it for free via hugging face here:

https://huggingface.co/Duskfallcrew/duskfall-alter-test

https://huggingface.co/Duskfallcrew/duskfall-alters-portrait-plus

https://huggingface.co/Duskfallcrew/Duskfall_Portraits_Epic_Train

If you want to donate towards costs and don't want to subscribe:

https://ko-fi.com/DUSKFALLcrew

If you want to monthly support the EARTH & DUSK media projects and not just AI:

https://www.patreon.com/earthndusk

ALTERS?

OOSDFOJS = PSHT...

WAHTEVER, YOU KNOW WE HAVE DISSOCIATIVE IDENTITY DISORDER -

We literally took all of our alters, plus our best friend's system, introjects, 3d faces and all and shoved it in. (Bar anyone who was 2d, illustrated or a picrew - or heavily edited)

modelVersions.name: 1.1- Epic Train
modelVersions.description:
Trained on Epic Diffusion, which worked fairly well. Because this is a better one than portrait plus for some reason - not that THE MODEL WE FINTUNED sucks but clearly we overbaked our finetune - this one is now the 1.1 rather than the other one.

THIS IS one of the big huge bases for EPIC MIX.

YES we'll finally get a safetensors for this soon.

modelVersions.name: 1.1 Portrait Plus

Am still hunting for a model that will make this work more with the aesthetic i'm looking for!
